item.title: LimeZ - Awake [Bounce/Trap]
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
Chords are a bit dissonant. Not sure I like it. Drums are cool though! Ilike how they switch up OFTEN! And when that drop hits! Woah! My only suggestion is that the chords be a little more varied with the next song. Pretty great track though!

Variation: 7/10
Creativity: 8/10
Predictability: 6/10
Use of Instruments/Automation: 6/10
Feeling: 8/10

Overall: 35/50
